events.name: QI｢イミセリノスの巫女からの依頼｣
イミセリノスの巫女からの依頼

parameters:
Nervous Imperial Soldier: U-um, do you have some business
with me?

Nervous Imperial Soldier: Do you have something you need
from me?

Cleric Sophia: I have come as a messenger of the Imiserinos
Shrine Maiden.

Nervous Imperial Soldier: I'm glad I've been praying every
day. Please listen to what I have to say!

Cleric Sophia: Are you trying to escape from military
service because you're scared... is that the reason?

Nervous Imperial Soldier: Before coming here, I was just
playing around with girls. And now I find myself in a place
where a hero like General Atu is coming...

Nervous Imperial Soldier: There are so many goblins, I
don't feel like I'll survive.

Cleric Sophia: How about running away? Even I don't want to
fight goblins.

Cleric Sophia: However, I have challenged and emerged
victorious against dragons with my companions for the sake
of our mission.

Nervous Imperial Soldier: Were you one of the companions of
the Dragon Slayer!?

Cleric Sophia: Cowardice and courage can coexist without
contradiction. The problem is whether you choose to have
courage or not, that's all.

Nervous Imperial Soldier: Thank you very much. I will do my
best to fight desperately for the Empire!
Nervous Imperial Soldier: Thank you, lovely lady!

Cleric Sophia: Hehe, it seems like it would be better to
fix your bad habits, don't you think?

Nervous Imperial Soldier: Hahaha, as an apology, please
take this.

Cleric Sophia: Thank you very much. May the blessings of
the goddess Imiserinos be upon you.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Nervous Imperial Soldier: I can't suddenly muster up
courage, but I'll do my best desperately for the Empire.
